metadata.name: End of Reality
metadata.description:
As they approached the event horizon, they immediately regretted their decision.
A cosmic entity was waiting for them at the end of the road, ready to absorb everything around them.
The powerful singularity is ready to take what belongs to it.
Is this the end or just the beginning?


The buyer will get a high res. file and the animated version of the piece.
